Class AeAbstractEntryPointVisitor

AeBPWSToWSBPELCorrelationInitiateVisitor, AeCreateInstanceMessageExchangeVisitor, AeCreateInstanceVisitor, AeDefEntryPointInitialVisitor
public abstract class AeAbstractEntryPointVisitor
extends AeAbstractDefVisitor

Abstract visitor for visiting entry point def objects in an AeProcessDef object.
Looks for receive activities and pick activities with onMessage children.
